<plot>Jane is giddy with excitement. After a picture-perfect date, the man of her dreams is sound asleep in her bed. As she anxiously waits in the dark for her prince to awaken, Jane's mind reels from the possibilities and to the pitfalls of their future as a couple, neurotically playing out their entire life together before it has a chance to begin. A darkly comic look the vagaries of relationships, especially when they're all in your head.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?081195</url></doc>
